    </div><a name="step1">&nbsp;</a><h2><span class="stepLabel">step 1</span><span class="stepTitle">Buy A Scrubbing Bubbles Automatic Shower Cleaner</span></h2><div class="txt"><div class="instructions">I'm a male college student, living in a house with 3 other male college
students...  One of our worst problems is cleaning.  The shower has
commonly grown so much mold that we usually felt much cleaner just not
taking a shower.  Thankfully, my roommates girlfriend bought us the
Scrubbing Bubbles Automatic Shower Cleaner. <br>
<br>
The thing works like a charm, attach it over your shower head, and once
a day, just push the little blue button and close the shower curtain...
after a few beeps the automated little maching shoots shower cleaner all
over the walls and tub. <br>
<br>
We haven't had to clean the shower yet in over 1.5 months!</div></div><a name="images"></a><div id="spot11166" class="image-spot"><div class='sizer'><img class='photo' src='/image/FKRK2D00USET9K5VED/Buy-A-Scrubbing-Bubbles-Automatic-Shower-Cleaner.jpg' GALLERYIMG='NO' alt='Buy A Scrubbing Bubbles Automatic Shower Cleaner' /></div></div>
